OL,3,CParents hid trackers in toys to see
OL,4,Cwhere kids 'could be snatched', judge
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FA mother and father sewed tracking
OL,8,Fdevices into their children's toys so
OL,9,Fthey could monitor where they were
OL,10,Fliving in foster care or from "where
OL,11,Fthey could be snatched", a Family
OL,12,FCourt judge has found.
OL,14,FAt the time the devices were
OL,15,Fdiscovered, the couple, who "give the
OL,16,Fimpression of being transient in their
OL,17,Flifestyles", had three children
OL,18,Ftogether, with the woman pregnant with
OL,19,Ftheir fourth.
