OL,3,CParents hid trackers in toys to see
OL,4,Cwhere kids 'could be snatched', judge
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe children, all younger than school
OL,8,Fage, are in foster care and the
OL,9,Fsubject of care proceedings.
OL,11,FIn May, the children's foster carers
OL,12,Ffound a small tracking device, made by
OL,13,Fthe same company as the mother's
OL,14,Fmobile phone, stitched into a bag
OL,15,Fwhich had been given to one of the
OL,16,Fchildren by their parents.
