OL,3,CParents hid trackers in toys to see
OL,4,Cwhere kids 'could be snatched', judge
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIn his judgment published on Friday,
OL,8,F12 September, Judge Malcom Sharpe said
OL,9,Fother items previously given to the
OL,10,Fchildren were also searched, and "two
OL,11,Ffurther devices were found, each in a
OL,12,Ftoy given to a child some weeks
OL,13,Fpreviously and each concealed by being
OL,14,Fsewn into the toy".
OL,26,@rD@bOUvD@RO]
