OL,3,CParents hid trackers in toys to see
OL,4,Cwhere kids 'could be snatched', judge
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe mother, who also has three older
OL,8,Fchildren ` two of whom live with
OL,9,Ffamily members, and one who has been
OL,10,Fadopted ` said she had planted the
OL,11,Ftrackers because she was concerned
OL,12,Fthat the children had attended
OL,13,Fmeetings with her "on a few occasions"
OL,14,Fwith bruising.
OL,16,FBut Judge Sharpe said she was unable
OL,17,Fto say "why she had thought that being
OL,18,Fable to locate the children and track
OL,19,Fthem would have assisted with regard
OL,20,Fto any bruising sustained".
