OL,3,CParents hid trackers in toys to see
OL,4,Cwhere kids 'could be snatched', judge
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"In fact, I am inclined to the view
OL,8,Fthat the father was probably the
OL,9,Fdriver behind what has turned out to
OL,10,Fbe a disastrous diversion from the
OL,11,Fprogress the case had been making."
OL,13,FHe added that he was "unhesitating" in
OL,14,Fconcluding that he could not "accept
OL,15,Fthe parents' evidence as to the
OL,16,Ftracking devices and therefore reject
OL,17,Fit".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@cO]uD@VOUuD@cO]vD@^OUyD@CO]
