OL,7,FThe judge concluded that the parents
OL,8,Fnow needed to "take stock" and reflect
OL,9,Fon his findings and "start to work out
OL,10,Fhow they can address the damage they
OL,11,Fhave caused" to their wider case
OL,12,Fsurrounding care of the children.
